#### XII

<div style="font-size: 90%">

The *Chiao T‘ung;* narrative. A woman scorning her lover.

</div>

<div style="margin-left: 20%; margin-right: 20%; font-size: 110%;">

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1">1</span></span>O dear! that
artful boy  
  Refuses me a word!  
But, sir, I shall enjoy  
  My food, though you're absurd!

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2">2</span></span>O dear! that
artful boy  
  My table will not share!  
But, sir, I shall enjoy  
  My rest, though you're not there!

</div>

